data.text:
Princess Marie Immaculata Elisabeth Rose Aldegunde of Liechtenstein 15 December 1991 as the daughter of Princess Marie Isabelle of Orleans, Princess of Liechtenstein and Prince Gundakar of Liechtenstein. Princess Leopoldine has three younger siblings:

-Princess Leopoldine Eleonore Therese Marie of Liechtenstein (1990), Prince Johann Wenzel Karl Emmeran Bonifatius Maria of Liechtenstein (1993), Princess Margarete Franciska Daria Wilhelmine Marie of Liechtenstein (1995), Prince Gabriel Karl Bonaventura Alfred Valerian Maria of Liechtenstein (1998)

She has following godparents: Prince Jean of Orleans, The Count of Paris, The Duke of Vendome (material uncle), Princess Aldegunde of Liechtenstein

She is godmother to her first cousin Princess Jacinthe Elisabeth-Charlotte Marie of Orleans, youngest daughter of the The Count and Countess of Paris.

Title

15 December 1991 Her Serene Highness Princess Marie Immaculata Elisabeth Rose Aldegunde of Liechtenstein, Countess of Rietberg
